                <note rend="inline" type="source">123H16/177: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-11-17T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 17, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3794. For Halstead.</p>
                <p>7. Your 39, November 12, 3 p.m.<note n="5" xml:id="d243fn5">Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <p>You will continue after the close of the Peace Mission in Paris in the capacity
                    of United States Commissioner until the sending of diplomatic and consular
                    representatives to Vienna.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
